
source code: dos_energy.py



Task
=======

Program to select only even indexed data rows. 

1. It combines data from two different input files in file 1
2. It takes only even indexed rows from newly generated file 1 and write them to a new file, file 2
3. It takes first 31 rows from file 1 and after that only even indexed rows and write them in file 3





Input
______

These input parameter must be updated inside dos_energy.py (line 13)

input_file1="1_RPDOS_W16_207_40_15_2_95_22.dat"
input_file2="1_W16_final-dos_Ei%3d300-130-30meV_dE%3d1.5-1.5-0.75meV_Ecut%3d207meV_Ec%3d95_22meV_W%3d1-0.txt"
no_of_lines = 320
output_file1= "1_W16_0.75meV"
output_file2= "2_W16_1.5meV"
output_file3= "3_W16_combined"


Process
_________
To run this code write command
python dos_energy.py



Output
______
1_W16_0.75meV.txt
2_W16_1.5meV.txt
3_W16_combined.txt
1_W16_0.75meV.xlsx
2_W16_1.5meV.xlsx
3_W16_combined.xlsx






